import React from 'react'
import { Box, Center, GluestackUIProvider, Heading, Image, Input, InputField, ScrollView, Text, VStack, View, } from '@gluestack-ui/themed'
import { config } from '@gluestack-ui/config'

export default function HomePage() {
  return (
    <GluestackUIProvider config={config}>
      <View backgroundColor='$primary0' flex={1}>
        {/* <Text color='$amber500' fontSize="3em" fontWeight="bold">NoteSketch</Text> */}
        <Center>
          <Image size="2xl" alignContent='center' justifyContent='center' source={require('../img/note.png')} marginTop={35} />
        </Center>


        <ScrollView borderTopRightRadius={50} borderTopLeftRadius={50} backgroundColor='$yellow200' flex={1} h={100} p="$6">
            <Box marginTop={30}>
              <VStack reversed={false}>
                <Center>
                  <Text size='4xl' marginBottom={30} fontWeight='$bold'>This is Topic</Text>
                </Center>
                <Text fontWeight='$bold'>Name</Text>
                <Input variant="underlined" size="lg" isDisabled={false} isInvalid={false} isReadOnly={false} >
                  <InputField
                    placeholder='Enter Text here'
                  />
                </Input>

              </VStack>
            </Box>
        </ScrollView>


      </View>
    </GluestackUIProvider>
  )
}
